Class EngineModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • at.fhhagenberg.mc.traffsim.vehicle.model.consumption.physics.EngineModel

  • public class EngineModel
extends java.lang.Object
    Container class providing a number of engine-related parameters and certain interfaces to access them in an abstracted manner.

    Christian Backfrieder
